sync,is,a,file,sharing,and,file,storage,application,for,web,desktop,and,mobile,Users,can,upload,sync,share,and,store,files,and,documents,across,multiple,platforms,The,sync,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,sync,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,accounts,adding,and,managing,files,and,retrieving,files